Package codes.thischwa.jii

Contain the basic interfaces and objects.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDimensionProvider
    Interface for beans which provides the Dimension of an image.
    IInfoProvider
    Interface for all beans, which provides properties of an image file.
    IResolutionProvider
    Interface for beans which provides the Resolution of an image.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Resolution
    Encapsulate the resolution of an image.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ImageType
    Hold informations about the different image types.
